content: 500 Entry passes to the ultimate trading education DAO. Built around growth, the community focuses on trading education while talking markets live day in day out. The DAO controls the treasury which has a continual funding stream of 100% of secondary sales royalties. The aim is to grow the treasury so all NFT holders begin to take yield.
